    "data": {
      "merge": "<ul><li><p>You have Resistance to fire damage.</p></li><li><p>Any fire damage you deal ignores Resistances.</p></li></ul>",
      "dismiss": "<p>When you dismiss this Arcanum, choose Forge or Inferno:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Forge.</strong> You create a basic armor, shield, or weapon of your choice (see <strong>Core Rulebook,</strong> pages <strong>130</strong> to<strong> 133</strong>). If you select this option again, the previously created item vanishes. If you create a weapon this way, it deals fire damage instead of physical.</p></li><li><p><strong>Inferno.</strong> Choose any number of creatures you can see: each of them suffers <strong>@DMG[30 fire]</strong> damage. This damage ignores Resistances.</p></li></ul>",
      "domains": "fire, heat, metal"
